Before Li Weihao left,

296
00:22:16,320 --> 00:22:17,360
I asked him

297
00:22:17,920 --> 00:22:19,850
to check Uncle Li's dash cam for me.

298
00:23:30,600 --> 00:23:31,880
Is this drug going to work?

299
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:33,340
What if she wakes up later?

300
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:34,280
Don't worry.

301
00:23:35,040 --> 00:23:36,000
This bit of sugar

302
00:23:37,080 --> 00:23:39,210
is enough to make her sleep for an hour.

303
00:23:40,600 --> 00:23:41,320
Old Li,

304
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:44,970
Sometimes I think you are quite ruthless.

305
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:46,080
You take girls

306
00:23:46,080 --> 00:23:47,720
the same age as your son

307
00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:49,400
to that kind of place every day.

308
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:50,800
Doesn't your conscience

309
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:51,720
hurt?

310
00:23:52,560 --> 00:23:54,040
I'm just a delivery guy.

311
00:23:55,040 --> 00:23:56,700
There are buyers and sellers.

312
00:23:57,360 --> 00:23:59,160
Why shouldn't I make this money?

313
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:01,320
Shasha.

314
00:24:01,320 --> 00:24:02,380
What are you doing?

315
00:24:07,400 --> 00:24:08,120
Shasha!

316
00:24:09,320 --> 00:24:10,800
I'm just a delivery guy.

317
00:24:11,760 --> 00:24:13,420
There are buyers and sellers.

318
00:24:14,120 --> 00:24:15,920
Why shouldn't I make this money?

319
00:24:17,480 --> 00:24:18,080
Shasha!

320
00:24:18,080 --> 00:24:19,140
What are you doing?

321
00:24:36,040 --> 00:24:37,960
I always thought he knew nothing.

322
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:40,130
It's not your fault.

323
00:24:41,160 --> 00:24:42,040
Maybe

324
00:24:42,240 --> 00:24:44,080
he just couldn't face the fact

325
00:24:44,080 --> 00:24:46,340
that his relative turned into a monster.

326
00:24:48,840 --> 00:24:49,920
Anyway,

327
00:24:52,480 --> 00:24:53,720
I used him.

328
00:24:58,280 --> 00:25:01,540
I was the one who made him see the other side of his relative.

329
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:02,760
And on his birthday,

330
00:25:04,440 --> 00:25:05,600
I broke his heart.

331
00:25:08,320 --> 00:25:09,520
I'm also responsible

332
00:25:11,040 --> 00:25:12,300
for Li Weihao's death.

333
00:25:28,680 --> 00:25:30,610
Zhang Chao, what's wrong with you?

334
00:25:41,120 --> 00:25:41,920
Are you okay?

335
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:43,600
I'll go get a rag.

336
00:25:51,120 --> 00:25:52,320
Why did you do this?

337
00:25:53,800 --> 00:25:54,520
What?

338
00:25:55,040 --> 00:25:55,760
Why?

339
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:57,800
Why?

340
00:25:58,160 --> 00:25:59,480
Zhang Chao, what's wrong with you?

341
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:01,520
Why did you hurt Xiaohao?

342
00:26:02,240 --> 00:26:04,560
Why did you use him?

343
00:26:04,560 --> 00:26:05,680
Bai Qiu.

344
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:07,440
Why did you do this?

345
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:09,040
Bai Qiu.

346
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:21,280
I'm sorry.

347
00:26:21,600 --> 00:26:22,360
Excuse me.

348
00:26:23,600 --> 00:26:25,460
I won't tell Uncle Li about today.

349
00:26:25,840 --> 00:26:27,100
Be careful from now on.

350
00:26:32,360 --> 00:26:34,200
Even though I have the dashcam,

351
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:36,860
I need more evidence before calling the police.

352
00:26:45,120 --> 00:26:45,840
Chen Rong.

353
00:27:00,040 --> 00:27:00,840
You're awake.

354
00:27:05,800 --> 00:27:07,000
You've had a long day.

355
00:27:07,360 --> 00:27:08,440
Have some chocolate

356
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:09,900
to replenish your energy.

357
00:27:10,120 --> 00:27:11,200
I don't like sweets.

358
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,400
I'm not a kid.

359
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:13,200
Just eat it.

360
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:15,650
It's nice to be a kid sometimes.

361
00:27:20,280 --> 00:27:21,440
A kid.

362
00:27:23,360 --> 00:27:25,000
Rice with chili sauce.

363
00:27:25,520 --> 00:27:27,920
Not many Qiongzhou people like spicy food.

364
00:27:29,920 --> 00:27:30,960
You stopped eating chili sauce

365
00:27:30,960 --> 00:27:32,290
and switched to sweets.

366
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:35,680
I know who Zhang Chao's alter ego is.

367
00:27:55,400 --> 00:27:59,560
Come catch me.

368
00:28:15,960 --> 00:28:17,040
I know who you are.

369
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:19,240
You are a split personality of mine.

370
00:28:19,240 --> 00:28:20,200
You are fake.

371
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:21,360
No.

372
00:28:21,800 --> 00:28:23,660
You are the one who doesn't exist.

373
00:28:23,720 --> 00:28:24,520
What did you say?

374
00:28:24,520 --> 00:28:26,080
You are the alter ego.

375
00:28:37,520 --> 00:28:40,120
You deserve it.

376
00:28:49,560 --> 00:28:52,080
Xiaochao, don't leave me.

377
00:28:52,080 --> 00:28:53,080
Xiaochao.

378
00:28:55,040 --> 00:28:55,970
What did you say?

379
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:58,040
What did you say?

380
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:00,320
You are nothing.

381
00:29:00,320 --> 00:29:01,600
Shut up.

382
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,050
Zhang Chao, I'm not.

383
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:12,240
I'm not.

384
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:13,520
Zhang Chao, who am I?

385
00:29:14,040 --> 00:29:15,000
Zhang Chao.

386
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:16,320
Zhang Chao, what's wrong with you?

387
00:29:16,320 --> 00:29:16,880
Zhang Chao.

388
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:17,400
No.

389
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,060
Zhang Chao.

390
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:19,370
Relax and look at me.

391
00:29:28,360 --> 00:29:29,890
Are you feeling any better?

392
00:29:32,200 --> 00:29:33,200
Are you okay?

393
00:29:39,800 --> 00:29:42,400
Do you remember the butterfly hug I taught you?

394
00:29:42,760 --> 00:29:44,090
Shall we do it together?

395
00:30:44,720 --> 00:30:45,640
No wonder.

396
00:30:47,320 --> 00:30:49,180
I don't have childhood memories.

397
00:30:50,120 --> 00:30:50,880
No wonder.

398
00:30:53,440 --> 00:30:55,440
I am nothing like the old Zhang Chao.

399
00:30:57,600 --> 00:30:58,760
You saw him.

400
00:31:05,040 --> 00:31:05,960
Ms. Chen.

401
00:31:14,280 --> 00:31:15,040
Who am I

402
00:31:15,040 --> 00:31:16,400
exactly?
